description:
Just in time for the holidays, here's a rendition of JOY TO THE WORLD karaoke style! Wether you're a festive person or just need a good laugh, this is the karaoke version for you!

If you're looking for a fun, festive karaoke version of the classic Christmas song, then look no further! This version is sung in reggae style, so you'll get that Caribbean feel in your Karaoke session! Enjoy!
Music performed by C Lalhmuaka, 3 Sisters  youtube production!
Note: You can use this instrumental for your covers just include credits and link of this video into your description. But registering it on paid site or post is not allowed.

Motion Graphics Used : Sis.Surangani Rosi - NAMADUMA https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCKJhoXuYEfnpHXLEIuH5CIw/videos
